name: Baby Hazel Lighthouse Adventure
description:
Hurray! Baby Hazel Lighthouse Adventure game is available in a bundle of 5 Baby Hazel Adventure Games. Download Now.

Kids can play Baby Hazel Lighthouse Adventure game for free.

Darling Baby Hazel is growing up fast. Looks like her imaginations are a delight to others. Do you want to experience her fantasies? They are so exciting and fun-filled. Join Baby Hazel in her fantasy world and experience a cruise ride and a life in the middle of waters. Oh, there is also a light house. What happens when our little princess gets inside? Shhh… it is a secret. You need to play and know it all by yourself.
